SSWL relies on a set-up of channel partners that are local and in tune with the areas of the city. This commitment to local community-oriented services puts SSWL at an advantage when compared to many of its competitors.

Sristisanchar Webnet Limited (SSWL) began with a working team of 5 members and is growing with considerable pace. The central vision of the company is to provide reliable, high-speed and efficient internet services to all regions of the city. It caters to an ever-increasing domestic and commercial customer service base. Its competitive prices and efficient team makes the company a reliable and sustainable choice.

SSWL's commitment to providing reliable internet stems from its consistent support to the endeavour to digitise India and make internet accessibility easier for all.

Hungama subscription includes 'Play' and 'Music'.

OTTs will only be provided if they are chosen - where relevant - on the same day that a package is renewed.

SSWL strongly recommends online renewal for seamless VAS / OTT activation.

OTTs are subject to availability, therefore SSWL reserves the right to remove / add any OTT(s) and amend plans without prior notice.

All OTT plans come with unlimited data transfer and an FTA module.
